OL,3,CFishing company fined #100,000 after
OL,4,Ctwo men died when boat sank
OL,6,FA fishing company must pay more than
OL,7,F#100,000 after a highly modified boat
OL,8,Fcapsized off the Sussex coast, causing
OL,9,Fthe deaths of two people onboard.
OL,11,FLaura D Fishing Ltd., a company
OL,12,Foperating fishing vessels from
OL,13,FBrixham, has pleaded guilty to failing
OL,14,Fto take all reasonable steps to ensure
OL,15,Fthat a vessel was operated in a safe
OL,16,Fmanner.
