OL,3,CFishing company fined #100,000 after
OL,4,Ctwo men died when boat sank
OL,6,FOn 21 November, 2020, Robert Morley,
OL,7,FAdam Harper and David Bickerstaff were
OL,8,Fonboard the Joanna C, five miles south
OL,9,Fof Newhaven, when the vessel's gear
OL,10,Fsnagged on the seabed.
OL,12,FThe vessel's lack of stability meant
OL,13,Fit could not recover, causing the
OL,14,FJoanna C to rapidly sink.
OL,16,FOut of the three crew members, only Mr
OL,17,FBickerstaff survived.
