OL,3,CFishing company fined #100,000 after
OL,4,Ctwo men died when boat sank
OL,6,FPrior to the incident, Joanna C, owned
OL,7,Fby Laura D Fishing, had undergone a
OL,8,Fmajor refit in 2019, including the
OL,9,Faddition of a whaleback, extension of
OL,10,Fthe wheelhouse and fitting raised
OL,11,Fbulwarks.
OL,13,FThese, along with other modifications,
OL,14,Faffected the stability of the vessel.
OL,16,FVessel modifications should only be
OL,17,Fcarried out following consultation
OL,18,Fwith, and approval of the Marine and
OL,19,FCoastguard Agency.
