OL,3,CFishing company fined #100,000 after
OL,4,Ctwo men died when boat sank
OL,6,FWest Hampshire Magistrates Court hear
OL,7,Fthat extensive changes made to Joanna
OL,8,FC, not approved by the MCA, made it
OL,9,Fsignificantly non-compliant with the
OL,10,Fminimum standards of stability.
OL,12,FThe vessel continued commercial
OL,13,Foperations however, without
OL,14,Fconsidering the impact and risks of
OL,15,Fthe modifications.
OL,17,FLaura D Fishing Ltd. was fined
OL,18,F#36,000, and ordered to pay #69,284 in
OL,19,Fcosts and a #190 surcharge.
