OL,3,CFishing company fined #100,000 after
OL,4,Ctwo men died when boat sank
OL,6,FThe MCA is reminding vessel owners
OL,7,Fthat their vessels must meet the
OL,8,Frequired safety standards despite
OL,9,Fchanges made, to avoid incidents like
OL,10,Fthis happening.
OL,12,FMark Cam, Senior Investigator with the
OL,13,FMCA, said: "This is a tragic reminder
OL,14,Fthat modifications to vessels should
OL,15,Fbe planned and their effects on the
OL,16,Fvessel's stability properly
OL,17,Finvestigated using appropriate
OL,18,Fprofessionals.
