OL,6,F"Companies are responsible for
OL,7,Fproviding a safe place of work for
OL,8,Ftheir employees, wherever that may be.
OL,10,F"The court has found that Laura D
OL,11,FFishing Ltd. did not take all
OL,12,Freasonable steps to operate the Joanna
OL,13,FC in a safe manner and this led to the
OL,14,Fdeaths of Adam and Robert."
